    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear what u mean about the orgs, but some of the parents i've talked to feel like it's not their place to teach this stuff at school and that it should be left to families. why do you say those concerns are mostly just due to misinformation though? isn't it a valid viewpoint to want to keep those topics out of the classroom?",
